<p>Dreaming of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> indicates good news, but seeing your cousin’s death or marriage, or your cousin’s engagement, or the birth of a new cousin, or anyone seeing a sick <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-عم-مريض-في-المنام?page=2729" >uncle</a> or a crying <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-عم-يبكي-في-المنام?page=2892" >uncle</a>, all these visions are different in meaning and we will explain them to you in detail about the unmarried, married, pregnant, divorced, and male daughter, and in detail for the great interpreters of dreams like <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" >Ibn Sirin</a>, al-Nabulsi, Fahad al-Asimi, and others.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >Cousins</a> in a dream</span></h2>
<p>We are talking about seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-أبناء-العمومة-في-المنام?page=3597" >cousins</a> in a dream, and among the beautiful visions in the case of dreams and visions, it is not only cousins, but also cousins, uncles and aunts from the male side. Praise be to Allah, the Great. <br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-ابن-عم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=658" >Seeing a cousin</a> in a dream is a vision that indicates an abundance of money, a large number of gains, and a large number of children.</p>
<p><span></span></p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
