</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>The marriage of your cousin in a dream, this vision indicates happy days in the coming period, God willing. <br/>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a>, this is a vision that indicates the presence of support from a family member. <br/>Whoever sees cousins gathered in the house, this vision indicates either hearing good news or meeting some problems that you have and want to solve, and it was said that a lot of happiness will happen in your life in general.</p>
<p>A <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> is also considered like a sister or a close friend, and seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-ابن-عم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=658" >cousin</a> in a dream indicates good news that will happen soon, or the benefit and benefit that will return to the insight, especially if the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> appears with a good appearance, clean clothes, and a happy and smiling face. <br/>The name of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> has a praiseworthy connotation in a dream, especially if their name is among the desirable names in the dream, as we mentioned earlier. <br/>And seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> in an unmarried woman's dream is a sign of marriage, and seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-حفل-زفاف-في-المنام?page=3962" >wedding</a> of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> in a dream reflects the insight in the sense that it indicates the marriage of the unmarried.</p>
<p>Your cousin in a dream has a special status like her sister or friend, she is a symbol of good news and often comes from the formulation of her name, for example.</p>
<p><span></span></p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
