</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>If you saw your cousin's daughter and her name was beneficial, this interpretation is a blessing that you will find in waking life. <br/>And if her name was Na'ima, this symbolizes the comfort of the world in terms of money and children. <br/>The best visions or dreams in which the cousin appears are those in which she smiles happily, or those in which you see her get married or succeed.</p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-ابن-عم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=658" >cousin</a> in a dream means that the person who sees the person is very dear and receives a lot of respect and love in their environment. everyone. <br/>Some researchers in dream interpretation believe that seeing your cousin's daughter in a dream indicates that the dreamer forms a great friendship with people suitable for the dreamer's mood and personality.</p>
<p>The cousin's illness symbolizes psychological problems or passing fears, while her death indicates positive changes that her cousin himself is going through, not the person in the dream.</p>
