<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> in a dream means that the dreamer will spend a good period without problems and experiences and will be able to pay off all his accumulated debts during previous periods, and his life will improve greatly. <br/>Whoever sees his cousin in his dream will get opportunities for plunder and achieve many positive changes in his life thanks to a relative, and he will live a life he has never lived before, and the conditions of the whole family will improve, especially the financial conditions. <br/>The vision also indicates an improvement in their work conditions and they will spend a happy and carefree life, achieve great success, and achieve a speedy recovery from all diseases, and their health will improve if they are sick.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>In general, seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-ابنة-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=1387" >cousin</a> in a dream is a sign of goodness, living, and blessings, as long as she appears in a worldly manner, with clean clothes, respectful behavior, and a beautiful and cheerful face.</p>
