</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-ابن-عم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=658" >cousin</a> in a dream shows the respect you will get from your family, and the person who sees a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> in a dream will gain appreciation and respect in the family, and he will be an example for the children of the family, who will take him as a role model for them.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of marrying a cousin in a dream</span></h2>
<p>It indicates gaining a suitable wife who fully fits the thinking of this dreamer and his personality. <br/>Dreaming of marrying a cousin also indicates the existence of an acquaintance between the two and that they are very similar to each other, and they will be a wonderful match for each other. <br/>It also indicates the end of crises and problems at the first opportunity to find joy and happiness again.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of kissing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-العم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=2397" >cousin</a> in a dream</span></h2>
<p>This person receives wonderful news that he was waiting for and waiting for, as the dreamer will meet with joy, happiness, and joy after his suffering from the problems and crises he faces. <br/>Some dreams related to kissing generally indicate luck and marriage, and for this reason, the dreamer may marry in a short period of time.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
