<p><span></span><strong>The neck in a dream, </strong><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-العنق-في-المنام?page=453" > seeing the neck </a> or the throat in a dream is one of the visions that carries many meanings and messages for the one who sees it.  The strength of faith and the observance of religious covenants, according to his condition in the dream, if he is sound and healthy.  Or suffering from a tumor or wound, all these details have different and varied meanings that we will mention through our website to answer the questions of viewers.</p>
