<h2><strong>The neck in a dream</strong></h2>
<p>Interpretive scholars have indicated that the wide neck that appears sound and strong is a symbol of the dreamer's truthfulness in promises, his preservation of trust and will, and that he is a strong believer and keen to fulfill his duties under any circumstances, in addition to perseverance and courage in facing enemies and dealing with them, whatever sacrifices it may cost him, or the tangible danger it entails.</p>
