</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>As for the neck suffering from a wound or a tumor, or the appearance of weakness and curvature in it, this is an indication of the dreamer's poor circumstances, betrayal of his promises, and betrayal of the trust placed in him, and he may be characterized by weakness of personality and his inability to face his enemies, which allows them to harm him in his work or in his family, and make his general life full of struggles and sorrows, and God knows best.</p>
