<p>The scholar <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> entered in his interpretations of seeing the neck in a dream into many details that play an important role in the diversity and multiplicity of sayings.  his inability to pay it or that he did not preserve the trust that was placed in him, but if he shaved this hair, this indicates the return of chests to their owners and improvement in his financial conditions, which will enable him. to pay debts.</p>
<p>The jurist also mentioned in his interpretations that the long beautiful neck is a praiseworthy sign of the improvement of the dreamer's circumstances, achieving what he aims for in strength, status, and acquiring material gains that bring him closer to his dreams.  and pursuits.. as he suffers from the accumulation of debts on his shoulders.</p>
