<h2><strong>The neck in a dream for an unmarried woman</strong></h2>
<p>Seeing a beautiful white neck in the dream of an unmarried woman proves that she will get rid of worries and sorrows and move to a new stage full of happiness and good news that the seer will hear soon.  Practically, she will find success with her partner, and her chances of being promoted to other departments will increase, and she will get the material and moral rewards she is aiming for, God willing.</p>
<p>The long beautiful neck is one of the promising signs for the girl to marry a good young man who will give her a comfortable and luxurious life, because he is likely to be one of the leading personalities who will occupy a prestigious position in society, and thus her living and social level will improve significantly. As for feeling the heaviness of her neck in the dream, it shows the size of the burdens and responsibilities that the girl bears alone and puts her in a circle of sadness and depression.</p>
<h2><strong>Seeing a lump on the neck in a dream for an unmarried woman</strong></h2>
