<h2><strong>The neck in a dream for a married woman</strong></h2>
<p>The neck in the dream of a married woman shows the trait of honesty and good morals, and her concern for the affairs of her home and children, and the fulfillment of her duties in the best way, or a negative impact on her life.</p>
<p>The dreamer hitting another woman on the neck violently and savagely is one of the indications of her desire for revenge and to regain her right from those who wronged her, and this may be reflected in her exposure to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-خيانة-الزوج-في-المنام?page=889" > infidelity </a> and control over anger.  and feelings that surpass her subconscious mind, or that the issue is related to the failure to regain trust from a close friend, which pushes her to take her right in violence and assault.</p>
<h2><strong>A wound on the neck in a dream for a married woman</strong></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الجرح-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=194" > Seeing the wound </a> on the neck carries many bad signs for a married woman, if the wound is superficial and there is no blood, this indicates that she was exposed to gossip and slander, or that she hears a lot of indecent words and insults.  The matter negatively affects her life and makes her feel ashamed and broken, and the need to regain her rights, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الجرح-المفتوح-في-المنام?page=3315" > the open wound </a> proves a lot of problems and suffering in her life.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
