<p>Some experts have also pointed out that the deep, painful wound in the neck is a bad sign of illness or the loss of a loved one close to the dreamer, so the dream is considered one of the signs of distress, sorrows, and dilemma.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><strong>Neck pain in a dream for a married woman</strong></h2>
