<p>The pain in the neck is also embodied in her feeling of guilt towards a wrong act she did in the past, but she cannot forget it and feels constant remorse. The pain in the neck is also embodied in her poor financial conditions and her inability. to pay off her debts or regain trust.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
