<p>Dreaming of a snail indicates happy changes, fulfillment of desires and other interpretations, and we will explain it for a single girl, a married woman, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > a pregnant woman </a>, a divorced woman, a married man and a single man, like seeing a slug or a snail without a shell, a snail in the hand or face, eating cooked snail, collecting snails, killing a white snail or <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> green and others in continuation of the topic:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the snail in a dream</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحلزون-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=409" > Seeing a snail </a> indicates a change in the situation, for example if it is a virgin girl or a young man, then this girl or young man will change their lives a lot and achieve all their ambitions.</p>
<p>Seeing a <strong>snail in a dream</strong> for traders means that the work of that trader is subject to loss and not profit, and for the trader who sees a snail in his dream, this indicates the failure of some deals due to stress.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
