<p>If he sees that he is eating a snail, he will live happily all his life and earn a lot. Also, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحلزون-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=409" > seeing a snail </a> eating in a dream indicates that you will enjoy happy times with friends and acquaintances. Seeing snails in your dream a lot symbolizes sex, marriage and changing circumstances.</p>
<p>A dream of a snail in a dream indicates movement from one place to another, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحلزون-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=409" > seeing a snail </a> indicates the need for self-care and protection.</p>
<p>The one who saw him <strong>living the snail in a dream</strong>, and this indicates that some positive things are not happening in your life because of shyness, lack of seriousness and boldness</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
