</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>A closed snail shows a period of contemplation and waiting for comfort, and the solution is not in your hands. If you see the snail extended to the maximum, this indicates reaching the limit of patience from the period of celibacy and the desire. get married.<br/>The snail can also indicate a comfortable and luxurious life that does not contain exhaustion, and the snail is also an indication of many trips and travel and a change of residence and lack of stability in one place.</p>
<p>A single girl who sees a snail in the house indicates good news about work, and a girl who sees a snail after rain and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-شروق-الشمس-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=38" > sunrise </a> indicates a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-زواج-قريب-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3121" > soon marriage </a>.<br/>The black or gray snail indicates fatigue, hardship, and toil in life.  <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحلزون-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=409" > Seeing a snail </a> is a sign of focusing on goals in your life that you intend to achieve.</p>
<p>The white snail means there is a happy event in the family, such as pregnancy or fulfillment of a wish.<br/>The snail in a dream of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant woman </a> is a positive symbol that foreshadows a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طفل-ذكر-لابن-سيرين?page=627" > male child </a> if it is white or green, and the snail also shows gentleness and safety and foreshadows a blessed birth for the pregnant woman.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
