<h2><span>Interpretation of the snail in a dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p>And Ibn Sirin says, the snail, if the dreamer sees it in a dream, this indicates that this person will travel, leave and migrate to any other place, and this vision differs from one person to another, so he can interpret the vision of that. snail for men and women.<br/>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحلزون-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=409" > snail </a> in a dream means, in all its meanings, healing, that is, it is a good vision.  It announces life in things with wonderful beauty and expresses new happy days to come.  It comes with the meaning of blessing, abundance, luck and good luck.  Whoever sees a snail in a dream will gain profit and see good even from the most desperate of works.  He will find comfort and blessings in his home life.  It also expressed that he will meet the lucky ones and deal with them.  Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحلزون-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=409" > snail </a> in a dream means that the owner of the vision will undertake, over time, long-term projects that bring him good.  The owner of the insight will get what he wants after he is patient.<br/>If you see a snail crawling in your dream, then you are surrounded by unhealthy and unfair situations, and if you step on a snail, you will deal with unpleasant and ill-tempered people.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحلزون-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=409" > Seeing a snail </a> in a dream means <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الانتقال-من-مكان-إلى-آخر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3204" > moving from one place to another </a>.  The scholar <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> said about the interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحلزون-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=409" > seeing a snail </a> in a dream or a snail in general, it is a sign of travel, migration, and displacement for the owner of this vision.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
