</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing a shell in a dream also indicates a change in circumstances in general and a change in conditions from one state to another.  For example, if it comes in a dream of an unmarried girl or an unmarried young man, it indicates a change in their lives for the better and the entry of a new stage in the actress in marriage.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing a shell in a dream indicates someone who is trading in a commercial project, this is an indication that his commercial project is at risk and that he is exposed to loss.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
