</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>If we dream of cooked snails, this indicates the occurrence of some events that may harm some people.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>As for eating a snail in a dream, it indicates happiness and pleasure that the owner of this vision may oppose.</p>
